children.subject:
How's the time/week in 162 compared to 170? (Which I'm taking right now)

I'm also doing 188 right now, and from what you're saying about 186 it sounds a lot like 188.

162 will take up a lot of your time. That in itself will still make your semester stressful. This stress could decrease depending on the talent and hard work your 3 teammates have and do. 186 is no joke, although maybe 2/5 of the assignments are decently chill, the other 3 are not. You have 2 weeks to complete each assignment, and could finish each in 2-5 days, but when a bug arises, it can be hard to find. The tests are also challenging, as they go beyond the lecture and discussions in terms of difficulty. When I took data 100, it was low workload and relatively easy, but I have heard differently.

Recruit, exercise, join a club, cooking a little...unless you're confident in your abilities, I recommend 162 and data 100. Well, I would recommend 186 and data 100 actually, but if you insist on 162..
